        "---\n",
        "# Scenario 1: RAG Pipeline\n",
        "*Retrieve context from a knowledge base, generate answer, evaluate everything.*"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 4,
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
